        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Ah yes truly a worth subject. The temple of Illuvatar has stood here before the time Tharbad was built. This was an ancient site of holy pilgrimage many an age ago. Since that time... the city has sprung up around its heels. And now dominates this once humble sanctuary. Now as the city of Tharbad falls into the hands of reputable characters. We hope to help ease the suffering of the less fortunate citizens."
